sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Wallet Unit as Wallet Unit
    participant OS/Browser as OS/Browser
    participant RP App as RP App
    participant RP BE as RP BE

    activate User
    User->>RP App: Pay for order with EUDIW
    activate RP App

    %% Payment Authorization
    RP App->>RP BE: Prepare Request URI with payment data
    activate RP BE
    RP BE-->>RP App: Request URI
    deactivate RP BE
    RP App->>RP App: Display QR code with deeplink
    deactivate RP App

    alt scan QR code (cross device)
        User->>Wallet Unit: Open camera
        Wallet Unit-->>RP App: Scan QR code with camera
        Wallet Unit->>Wallet Unit: Process scaned request
    else click on deeplink
        User->>RP App: Click on deeplink QR code
        activate RP App
        RP App->>OS/Browser: Open deeplink
        deactivate RP App
        activate OS/Browser
        opt More Wallets in OS
            User->>OS/Browser: Choose "Wallet Unit"
        end
        OS/Browser->>Wallet Unit: Invoke with Openid4VP request
        deactivate OS/Browser
    end

    activate Wallet Unit
    Wallet Unit->>RP BE: POST /par (with Wallet Metadata)
    Note left of RP BE: We instigate that merchant will use<br/>only reference to Request Object<br/>and Request data will be downloaded<br/>from "RP BE" server see<br/>5.10. Request URI Method POST in OpenID4VP
    activate RP BE
    RP BE-->>Wallet Unit: OpenID4VP encrypted request
    deactivate RP BE
    
    Wallet Unit->>Wallet Unit: Decrypt and validate credential request
    
    opt vct metadata cache empty
        loop vct in payment credentials
            Wallet Unit->>Issuer: Get SD-JWT vct metadata
            activate Issuer
            Issuer-->>Wallet Unit: vct metadata
            deactivate Issuer
        end
        Wallet Unit->>Wallet Unit: Evalute credential eligibility for payment type
    end
    
    Wallet Unit->>Wallet Unit: Display Payment
    User->>Wallet Unit: Confirm Payment & authenticate for SUA key
    Wallet Unit->>Wallet Unit: Attach transaction data KB-JWT to SUA presentation, create final VP token
    Wallet Unit->>Wallet Unit: Encrypt with Merchant public key
    Wallet Unit->>RP BE: /POST response_uri from request
    Note left of RP BE: Direct_post.jwt with signed and encrypted response must be used,<br/>also validation on response domain given request by Merchant
    activate RP BE
    RP BE-->>Wallet Unit: deeplink redirect to "RP App"
    deactivate RP BE
    
    Wallet Unit->>OS/Browser: Deeplink redirect to "RP App"
    activate OS/Browser
    OS/Browser-->>RP App: Invoke "RP App" with redirect
    deactivate OS/Browser
    activate RP App
    RP App->>RP App: Continue with merchant flow
    deactivate RP App
    deactivate User
